data.description: **Condo has reserves** Updated 2 bed/2.5, 2 bath, 2 level home in Foxcroft Miramar. Unit has been updated and features tile floors throughout living area, and laminate wood floors upstairs in the bedrooms and hallway.  Remodeled kitchen, remodeled bathrooms, balcony with view of the  pool and garden. Unit has an open floor plan and one of few units to have a 2 story! Community is very well kept with community pool, playgrounds, brand new Common Laundry on each floor, next to unit and much more. Centrally located to Highways, Supermarkets, Shopping and Schools. Association requires clean background and 630 credit score. Please see attached required disclosures.  Please ask about credit toward closing costs or rate buy down. *Asso fee includes water, roof,ext insurance!* Bring all offers*
